    b"rent user request.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Use the available task information and context to "
    b"decide which task should\x0d\x0a        run next.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Context sections:\x0d\x0a      "
    b"  - Current user request: the request being routed now.\x0d\x0a        - Conversation "
    b"history: earlier human and agent messages from this session.\x0d\x0a        - Session "
    b"memories: remembered observations for this session.\x0d\x0a        - Available tasks: "
    b"the only tasks that may be selected.\x0d\x0a        - Task-choice memories: remembered"
    b" observations about choosing tasks.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Optional outputs available in thi"
    b"s step:\x0d\x0a        - agent_thought: private context to add to the conversation wit"
    b"hout\x0d\x0a          notifying the human.\x0d\x0a        - candidate_memory: a vague rememb"
    b"ered observation that could be useful to\x0d\x0a          preserve.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Rules:\x0d"
    b"\x0a        - Select exactly one task from Available tasks.\x0d\x0a        - selected_tas"
    b"k_id must exactly match an available task id.\x0d\x0a        - Do not invent task ids."
    b"\x0d\x0a        - Do not perform the task. Only choose the task.\x0d\x0a        - Use option"
    b"al outputs only when they are useful.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Current user request:\x0d\x0a        "
    b"{{ current_user_request }}\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Conversation history:\x0d\x0a        {% for conv"
