    b"versationMemorySearchHints\x00\x00\x01\x00\xba\x0e\x00\x00\x0a        {{ _.role(\"system\") }}\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        You"
    b" evaluate the current conversation and produce memory search hints for\x0d\x0a        "
    b"the selected task.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        The hints will drive memory search before the sele"
    b"cted task runs.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Stop once the hints look good enough for the request "
    b"without thinking about it too much.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Search surfaces:\x0d\x0a        - tags:"
    b" exact memory tags. They are not substring searched.\x0d\x0a        - strings.contains"
    b": case-insensitive text fragments. Each value is checked\x0d\x0a          as a substri"
    b"ng against searchable memory content.\x0d\x0a        - strings.equals: exact text valu"
    b"es. Each value is checked for exact\x0d\x0a          equality against searchable memor"
    b"y content.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Optional outputs available in this step:\x0d\x0a        - candid"
    b"ate_memory: a vague remembered observation that could be useful to\x0d\x0a          pr"
    b"eserve.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Rules:\x0d\x0a        - Return only search hints and optional candi"
    b"date_memory.\x0d\x0a        - Search hints are alternatives during retrieval; a memory"
    b" can be useful\x0d\x0a          when any positive tag or string hint matches.\x0d\x0a       "
    b" - Prefer tags.any_of for positive tag hints.\x0d\x0a        - Leave tags.all_of empty"
    b" unless compatibility with older memories needs it.\x0d\x0a        - Use tags.none_of "
    b"only for clear exclusions.\x0d\x0a        - Use strings.contains for durable words or "
    b"phrases that should appear\x0d\x0a          inside a relevant memory.\x0d\x0a        - Use s"
    b"trings.equals only for exact text that should match a relevant\x0d\x0a          memory"
    b" value as a whole.\x0d\x0a        - Prefer a small set of high-signal hints over broad"
    b" keyword stuffing.\x0d\x0a        - Return empty arrays when no useful search hint is "
    b"available.\x0d\x0a        - Use optional outputs only when they are useful.\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a       "
    b" {{ _.role(\"user\") }}\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Current user request:\x0d\x0a        {{ current_user_"
    b"request }}\x0d\x0a\x0d\x0a        Conversation history for the current session:\x0d\x0a        {% "
